{"kind":"performance","model_id":"eleven_v3","source":"/Users/dusty/Dev/metaphrand/.claude/worktrees/rosca-pitch/stories/four-olds/audio/a28_sendoffs.scene.txt","lines":[{"i":2,"role":"CRICKET","text":"(reading) Logbook. Slide rule."},{"i":5,"role":"DANNY","text":"[quietly] I know what's in the barn, Dad. I've known about a year now. Figured you'd say something when it got to where it mattered."},{"i":7,"role":"DANNY","text":"I'm not going to say any of the things. Your age, or the law, or Mom. [pause] You'd just stand there and let me get all the way through it."},{"i":8,"role":"CRICKET","text":"[flatly] I would."},{"i":11,"role":"DANNY","text":"County's squared, by the way. Paid it Tuesday, so that's handled."},{"i":13,"role":"CRICKET","text":"[quietly] I'll pay you back."},{"i":14,"role":"DANNY","text":"I know."},{"i":16,"role":"DANNY","text":"You need a driver, or."},{"i":17,"role":"CRICKET","text":"[flatly] Thursday. Four a.m. Dress like a farmer."},{"i":18,"role":"DANNY","text":"I am a farmer."},{"i":21,"role":"CRICKET","text":"[hesitates] You'll want the..."},{"i":24,"role":"CRICKET","text":"(low) [quietly] Something's sewn in here."},{"i":27,"role":"CRICKET","text":"(low) [quietly] ...A zinnia."},{"i":38,"role":"LITA","text":"(close) [warmly] Cuídate, mijo."},{"i":40,"role":"TITO","text":"(close) [quietly] Sí, abuela."}]}